latestIgtvVideos.caption: To the woman made of steel, my mother. Who’s silent support helps me keep my head held high, who's safety net helps me live without fear. The woman who taught me how to love wholeheartedly and unconditionally. My personal rock of Gibraltar! My inspiration! My motivation! My friend! My guide! My everything! I wouldn’t be me without you. And life would be a whole lot duller if you weren’t my mama! I love you! @buntybajaj

latestPosts.caption:
A beautiful afternoon at an intimate fundraising lunch in New Jersey, hosted by a dear friend in support of @mudita_tribe 💛 We were deeply moved by the community’s response—people from all walks of life came together, took time out of their busy schedules, and contributed with such open hearts.

A special shoutout to the younger generation who not only showed up but expressed a genuine interest in being part of Mudita’s future initiatives. Your energy, compassion, and commitment give us so much hope for what lies ahead.💫

Over a generous spread of home-cooked Andhra food, we shared stories, laughter, and a collective purpose. Our hearts are full. Thank you for making this such a meaningful day. 🙏🏻✨
